snippet.title: The GOAT (Official Trailer) Tamil: Thalapathy Vijay | Venkat Prabhu | Yuvan Shankar Raja | T-Series

Jaan Nisar Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 17th August 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

snippet.title: World‚Äôs Deadliest Battle | The Mahabharat Series | Ep 1 | Vikram Aditya  | Telugu
snippet.description:
Welcome to the first episode in our series on the Mahabharat, one of the greatest epics ever written. In this drama, we delve into the profound truth that there are no purely good or bad people, only good and bad circumstances.
In this episode, we explore Vyasa's visionary experience that led to the creation of this timeless epic. Discover how Vyasa, after dividing the Vedas, received a haunting vision of a catastrophic war‚ÄîThe Mahabharat. Disturbed and eager to document every detail, Vyasa chose the only being capable of keeping up with his narration, Lord Ganesha, to write down the untold story of his descendants.
Our storytelling is not just about revisiting ancient tales; it's about extracting timeless wisdom to confront modern challenges. This episode lays the foundation for understanding the Mahabharat's depth, where virtue and vice intertwine, revealing critical life lessons.

snippet.title: Mahindra Thar Roxx 5 door - Every Detail | AutoYogi | ICN Studio
snippet.description: Mahindra Thar‚Äôs 5-door version - Roxx - was finally launched in India on the evening of India‚Äôs 77th Independence Day. Similar to the 3-door version, it‚Äôs based on the same Scorpio N platform but several changes has been made to it to accommodate an extra row of seats and a bigger boot. The vehicle‚Äôs cabin too has seen an overhaul as it receives a revised dashboard layout that now accommodates a new 10.25-inch touchscreen, a 10.25-inch instrument cluster screen, soft touch material on top of the dash, a 360 degree camera, ventilated seats, electrically-adjustable driver seat, auto-dimming IRVM, panaromic sunroof, harmon-kardon music system, wireless charger, wireless apple carplay and android auto among others. So far we only know the prices of its base variants, the petrol base costs Rs 12.99 lakh (ex-showroom) and the diesel base costs Rs 13.99 lakh (ex-showroom). More details on its performance will be updated on 17th August. Stay tuned for that.

Double Ismart Shankar Box office collection,

In this video, we delve into the box office collections of some of the recent blockbuster movies in Bollywood and South Indian cinema.

Khel Khel mein 1st Day Box office collection,
Akshay Kumar's Comedy Drama entertainer "Khel Khel mein," Direct by Mudassar Aziz. the film has been creating waves at the box office with its high-octane action sequences and gripping storyline. ans Great Cast Including Ammy Virk Pragya Jaiswal Fardeen Khan Vaani Kapoor. The film has garnered impressive numbers at the box office, cementing Akshay Kumar's position as one of the top actors in the industry. Fans and critics alike have praised his performance in the movie, leading to a stellar box office collection. Khel Khel mein Movie Review & Khel Khel Mein Public review Coming Up,

Vedaa  Box office collection Day 1,
John Abraham starrer "Vedaa,"  Directed By Nikhil Advani a thrilling crime drama that has been a hit among audiences. John Abraham & Sharvari intense portrayal of his character has resonated with viewers, resulting in a strong box office performance for the film. "Vedaa" has proven to be a commercial success, showcasing John Abraham's star power and acting prowess. 
Vedaa Public Review & Veda Movie Review Out Soon,


Stree 2 movie Box office collection,
Shraddha Kapoor's horror-comedy "Stree 2," Directed By Amar Kaushik the film has been a favorite among audiences for its unique blend of humor and scares. Shraddha Kapoor's Pankaj Tripathi Rajkumar Rao stellar performance coupled with a captivating storyline has propelled "Stree 2" to great heights at the box office. The film's box office collection reflects the audience's love for this genre-bending film.
Stree 2 Movie Review & Stree 2 Public Review Coming Up,

Thanglaan Box office collection All Languages Worldwide,
Chiyaan Vikram's action thriller "Thanglaan," which has been making waves at the worldwide box office. Chiyaan Vikram's versatile acting and the film's gripping narrative have captured the audience's attention, leading to a strong box office performance globally. "Thanglaan" showcases Chiyaan Vikram's star power and acting chops, solidifying his position as a powerhouse performer in the industry.
Thangalaan Movie Hindi Review In Out Soon,

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 19 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 15th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Kaffara Episode 19 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 15th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Mufasa: The Lion King | Hindi Trailer | Shah Rukh Khan, Aryan Khan, AbRam Khan | In Cinemas Dec 20
snippet.description:
‡§¨‡§∏ ‡§è‡§ï ‡§π‡•Ä ‡§π‡•ã‡§ó‡§æ ‡§ú‡§Ç‡§ó‡§≤ ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§æ üëë
The King Shah Rukh Khan is back as Mufasa ü¶Å , with #AryanKhan and #AbRamKhan by his side
Mufasa: The Lion King in cinemas on 20th December, 2024

Exploring the unlikely rise of the beloved king of the Pride Lands, ‚ÄúMufasa: The Lion King‚Äù enlists Rafiki to relay the legend of Mufasa to young lion cub Kiara, daughter of Simba and Nala, with Timon and Pumbaa lending their signature schtick. Told in flashbacks, the story introduces Mufasa as an orphaned cub, lost and alone until he meets a sympathetic lion named Taka‚Äîthe heir to a royal bloodline. The chance meeting sets in motion an expansive journey of an extraordinary group of misfits searching for their destiny‚Äîtheir bonds will be tested as they work together to evade a threatening and deadly foe. 
 
Cast members that lent their voices to the film:
Shah Rukh Khan as Mufasa
Aryan Khan as Simba
AbRam Khan as Young Mufasa
Sanjay Mishra as Pumbaa
Shreyas Talpade as Timon
 
With an all-star roster of talent bringing new and fan-favorite characters to life, the film also has celebrated award-winning songwriter Lin-Manuel Miranda is writing the film‚Äôs songs produced by Mark Mancina and Miranda, with additional music and performances by Lebo M. 
 
Said Miranda, ‚ÄúElton John. Tim Rice. Hans Zimmer. Lebo M. Mark Mancina. Beyonc√©, Labrinth, Ilya Salmanzadeh. Beau Black, Ford Riley, the incredible music team on ‚ÄòThe Lion Guard,‚Äô and so many musical contributors over the years. ‚ÄòThe Lion King‚Äô has an incredible musical legacy with music from some of the greatest songwriters around, and I'm humbled and proud to be a part of it. It's been a joy working alongside Barry Jenkins to bring Mufasa's story to life, and we can't wait for audiences to experience this film in theaters."
 
Blending live-action filmmaking techniques with photoreal computer-generated imagery, ‚ÄúMufasa: The Lion King‚Äù is directed by Barry Jenkins, produced by Adele Romanski & Mark Ceryak, and executive produced by Peter Tobyansen.

snippet.title: Google Pixel 9 Pro XL is pushing the limits... (Durability Test)
snippet.description:
Today we durability test the new Pixel 9 Pro XL. Get a screen protector before you need one: https://www.dbrand.com/pixel-9-series The google pixel 9 XL has quite possibly the worlds largest camera bump. Its not even a bump at this point - its a plateau. But... the rest of the flat glass design makes up for the giganticness of the camera units.  Plus... bigger cameras usually mean better pictures. But Ill let other reviewers handle the software side of new Pixel phones.  We are here to test the durability of the Pixel 9 pro XL to see if it can really handle 7 years worth of use. 

Get my teardown skin for your phone HERE: https://www.dbrand.com/teardown
